name: Ulu Space Note Card
description:
Ulu Space Note Card with Envelope - Fold and Stand

This is a chance to buy a professionally printed notecard with envelope featuring an intricate multimedia artwork by me, Belinda Wilson. The work features embroidery, collage, painting and ink drawing.

These square prints have a special flap on the side, helping them to stand upright for display. Less formal than a greeting card, more fun than a Postcard, perfect for sending to friends.

Width: 142 mm
Height: 100 mm
Paper: 350g/m2
Finish: Laminated one side

Note cards are placed in a protective sleeve and posted in a stiff mailer.

Artist retains all reproduction rights and copyrights.
